text: Обаяние Чонгука идёт из его органики, потому что его поцеловал Господь и одарил его редким умением любить, отдавать, а не брать! Он интроверт, но без второго дна. Редко  кому подходит определение милый, как Чонгуку. Он умиляет своей искренностью и естественностью настоящей, а не напускной. Он настоящий, потому что хочет быть, а не казаться, как некоторые профессиональные актёры. Он ЧУДО!

text: It was amazing that we got a deep conversation about singing from Jungkook. We've been waiting for this for so long.  You can see how much he knows about his own voice and its different tones, and how languages ​​affect his voice!  The interview revealed his singing knowledge and the way he discovers his own style....Anyone who reads Jungkook's interview today knows that he is a passionate, hardworking and educated person, not only as a musician as a human being. This interview made us see his view of many things and how he is really a caring and educated person. No matter how famous he is, he continues to develop himself, despite all the difficulties he faced from debuting now and the pressures he went through until now... perfect people like Jungkook always feel that they are not giving their best or lazy as he says simply because they are able to give better than that and they are able to achieve perfection.  His words are not a disparagement of his person.. but there is noperfect person to come out and say, oh me So perfect.. but a person who is honest and humble like this.. I am proud of him, his personality, his way of thinking, his wisdom as a human being and as an artist, and I love him more and more
